{
  "page": "Bank of Oldtown",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Bank of Oldtown</b> is a bank run by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bank_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Rogare_Bank\" title=\"Rogare Bank\">Rogare Bank</a> collapsed in <a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136&#160;AC</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lotho_Rogare\" title=\"Lotho Rogare\">Lotho Rogare</a> was taken into the service of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Samantha_Tarly\" title=\"Samantha Tarly\">Samantha Tarly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Paramour\" title=\"Paramour\">paramour</a> and step-mother of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Hightower\" title=\"Lyonel Hightower\">Lyonel Hightower</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> had not entrusted its <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> to the bank, and remained one of the wealthiest <a href=\"/index.php/List_of_Houses\" title=\"List of Houses\">Houses</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>. Lady Samantha wished to learn how to invest better, and founded the Bank of Oldtown, which made House Hightower even richer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It is unknown whether the bank has persisted to this day.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bank_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">In <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_Regent\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen Regent\">Queen Regent</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a> thinks the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> needs a <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a> bank to thwart the influence of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Bank_of_Braavos\" title=\"Iron Bank of Braavos\">Iron Bank of Braavos</a> over the crown's <a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">treasury</a>. She imagines the creation of the \"Golden Bank of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>\", but does not mention the Bank of Oldtown <i>(<a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 36\">AFFC, Cersei VIII</a>)</i>. However, it is possible that the Bank of Oldtown is still active, but Cersei deliberately does not mention it, not trusting <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> and preferring to found a new bank to be controlled by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>. That being said, since the Bank of Oldtown was introduced in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> in 2018, it is likely <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> had not came up with the idea of a Hightower bank yet when he wrote <i>A Feast for Crows</i>, published in 2005.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bank_of_Oldtown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Commerce_and_Banking\" title=\"Template:Commerce and Banking\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Commerce_and_Banking&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Commerce and Banking (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Commerce_and_Banking&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nCommerce and banking organizations</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bank of Oldtown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Bank_of_Braavos\" title=\"Iron Bank of Braavos\">Iron Bank of Braavos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rogare_Bank\" title=\"Rogare Bank\">Rogare Bank of Lys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> merchant guilds:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ancient_Guild_of_Spicers\" title=\"Ancient Guild of Spicers\">Ancient Guild of Spicers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Thirteen\" title=\"Thirteen\">Thirteen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tourmaline_Brotherhood\" title=\"Tourmaline Brotherhood\">Tourmaline Brotherhood</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404203052\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.037 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.060 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 465/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 15755/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7743/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument siz